title: Confessions Of My Dangerous Mind 2014, 5th Iranian Film Festival Australia 2015

sources.title: ConfessionsOfMyDangerousMind20145thIranianFilmFestivalAustralia2015
sources.description: Synopsis A man wakes up in the middle of nowhere, not remembering his name. He can't remember if he's an addict, or he has cancer or maybe he just looks like it. That's why he enters the game that's been set up for him.
